'''Aba''' was one of a pair of [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] dolls given to [[Darth Caedus|Jacen]] and [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] by [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] after returning from a visit to [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]], that had occurred prior to their visit to [[Munto Codru/Legends|Munto Codru]] in [[14 ABY/Legends|14 ABY]]. Jacen named his doll Aba while Jaina's was [[Eba]].

